title: Superman Post-Crisis Chronology Collection, Fixes 2016-02-20
description:
From the OP:
"Fixes and patches.  Some alterations for continuity/readability (003), a rename (061), adding in some missing Superman Confidential issues (334,335), reordering volumes for better continuity surrounding The Obsidian Age event, prologue and epilogue (and in some cases the stories inside, 261-270), a massive update of most of the Supergirl v4 issues with the digitals that have been released since these volumes were and the rest are minor cover numbering fixed."
